      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) for use with network management protocols in the Internet community.  In particular, it describes managed objects used for logging Simple Network Management Protocol (SNMP) Notifications. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
